**Hashes**

JSON is a way of structuring data. The acronym stands for JavaScript Object Notation.
A very basic example of a simple JSON structure is:

{ "objectname": "objectdata" }

https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/JSON for more information.

Zerotalk is a forum built by [[nofish]]. It allows for users to create topics and participate in conversations. It uses [[markup]] to allow for rich text.

The site itself can be found [Here](http://127.0.0.1:43110/Talk.ZeroNetwork.bit/).

Client side is code, or an operation executing upon a client machine rather than server. As an example, a server sends a client browser javascript, the browser runs the javascript on the clients machine through the web browser.
